 and human trafficking offences</li>\n  <li>promote an improved law enforcement and criminal justice response to modern slavery across the UK</li>\n  <li>engage with the private sector and promote policies to ensure that supply chains are free of slavery</li>\n  <li>foster constructive and targeted international collaboration to combat modern slavery.</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-06-27T08:48:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Independent Anti-Slavery Commissioner","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-06-27T13:25:55Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Sara Thornton - Independent Anti-Slavery Commissioner","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-06-27T08:58:14Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Sara Thornton","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sara-thornton","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D16","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/home-office","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/home-office","base_path":"/government/organisations/home-office","content_id":"06056197-bc69-4147-aa28-070bca132178","details":{"acronym":"Home Office","brand":"home-office","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/669fa7f5ce1fd0da7b592afc/s960_2MS_Home_Office_sign_-_landscape.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/669fa7f5ab418ab055592b21/s300_2MS_Home_Office_sign_-_landscape.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"ho","formatted_title":"Home Office"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Home Office","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"dce6b9e6-bf38-4309-9baf-1fa5da78e113","details":{"body":"<p>The role was created as part of the landmark Modern Slavery Act 2015 and has a UK-wide remit to give independent advice on modern slavery issues and how they should be addressed.</p>\n\n<p>The Commissioner is expected to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>encourage good practice to increase the identification and protection of victims of modern slavery, \nand to ensure the provision of enhanced support for all victims and survivors in the UK</li>\n  <li>enable effective prevention of slavery and human trafficking offences</li>\n  <li>promote an improved law enforcement and criminal justice response to modern slavery across the UK</li>\n  <li>engage with the private sector and promote policies to ensure that supply chains are free of slavery</li>\n  <li>foster constructive and targeted international collaboration to combat modern slavery.</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-06-27T08:48:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Independent Anti-Slavery Commissioner","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"IM1123","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/independent-anti-slavery-commissioner","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/independent-anti-slavery-commissioner","base_path":"/government/organisations/independent-anti-slavery-commissioner","content_id":"cc338777-40c1-4b8c-9167-0e90739dfa3c","details":{"acronym":"IASC","brand":"home-office","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Independent Anti-slavery Commissioner"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.antislaverycommissioner.co.uk/"}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Independent Anti-slavery Commissioner","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/independent-anti-slavery-commissioner","withdrawn":false}],"primary_p